    {
      "id": "ppbPht-1FLdkDsl45N7sv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2890.74466865159,
      "y": 2005.3585253300796,
      "width": 834.9483032226562,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1079936511,
      "version": 324,
      "versionNonce": 1460457329,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777155632443,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Dicta que es incompatible combinar estas tres\ncaracteristicas en un sistema distribuido:\n    - C = Consistencia\n    - A = Availability (Disponibilidad)\n    - P = Tolerancia a particionado",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Dicta que es incompatible combinar estas tres\ncaracteristicas en un sistema distribuido:\n    - C = Consistencia\n    - A = Availability (Disponibilidad)\n    - P = Tolerancia a particionado",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "APs0iUzc37lV45eeK-tXP",
      "type": "rectangle",
